[Five deaths of children among 35 cases is an extraordinarily high case/fatality ratio. It suggests deficiencies in surveillance.

Chibia is a town and municipality in Huila province in Angola. A map of Angola showing the location of Huila can be accessed at: http://www.mapsofworld.com/angola/angola-political-map.html. - Mod.CP

